overview: Snapchat is an American multimedia messaging app developed by Snap Inc. originally Snapchat Inc. One of the principal features of Snapchat is that pictures and messages are usually only available for a short time before they become inaccessible to their recipients. The app has evolved from originally focusing on person-to-person photo sharing to presently featuring users Stories of 24 hours of chronological content.
